snippet.title: The Fateful Saint's Love Prologue
snippet.description: Honestly, I'm only interested in Cecil. I don't care for Ernest, and Lancelot kinda irritated me throughout the prologue so whether I do Lancelot depends on how well they portray him in Cecil's route.
